{"tid":2339813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國疫情燒不停！北京無症狀感染者趴趴走","createTime":"2020-12-25T03:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T12:41:45.000Z","uid":337052,"like":113,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"2315d6e8b464124d5f2fc0fa01d1ccec4db5e82f","tid":2339813,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:10:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">武漢肺炎》遼寧疫情燒不停！北京無症狀感染者趴趴走</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/12/25/phpYeCmGI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F12%2F25%2FphpYeCmGI.jpg&h=39aa0f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國24日再度新增確診病例14例，無症狀感染者17例，其中遼寧出現7例本土確診與1例本土無症狀感染者，北京也出現1例本土無症狀感染者，引發熱議。圖為北京地鐵。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n2020/12/25 10:51<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕年關將至，<span class=\"red\">中國武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情仍持續延燒，昨（24日）再度新增確診病例14例，無症狀感染者17例，其中遼寧出現7例本土確診與1例本土無症狀感染者，北京也出現1例本土無症狀感染者，引發熱議。</span><br />\n<br />\n根據中國衛健委公告，<span class=\"red\">昨（24日）0時至24時，中國31個省（自治區、直轄市）和新疆生產建設兵團報告新增確診病例14例（遼寧7例、境外輸入7例），新增無症狀感染者17例（遼寧1例、北京1例、境外輸入15例），新增疑似病例3例。</span><br />\n<br />\n其中，北京本土無症狀感染者為1名男性，12月6日自天津來京，從事冷鏈相關工作，也是某餐館員工，期間如常活動，直到22日北京市西城區對冷鏈從業人員展開例行核酸檢測，23日呈現陽性結果，當即由120負壓救護車急送至地壇醫院，經一系列檢查後於24日診斷為無症狀感染者，目前已對其密切接觸者進行集中隔離醫學觀察，也對其工作和居住等場所進行消毒，並落實相關管控措施。<br />\n<br />\n對此，中國網友紛紛傻眼表示，<span class=\"red\">「又是金融街」、「這還不算本土？」、「直接市中心了」、「跟兒童醫院只有一街之隔」、「病毒就像警察一樣，所有地方都管」、「北京的冷鏈有污染」、「我膽子小，明天要帶護目鏡上班了」</span>，不過也有人質疑，<span class=\"red\">「包裝帶病毒的冷凍海產品賣到北京了？」、「不主動檢測就不會發現，現在無症狀的估計不少吧！大年底都老實點吧！」。</span>"},{"pid":"34acdb6acc260735ad09c9955269463c8967d22b","tid":2339813,"uid":337052,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:10:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3391787\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3391787&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt0PclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=49ebcf76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3391787&h=d9483128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3391787</a>"},{"pid":"110b8f49673ff690d1dea19d3c129515fe61fce4","tid":2339813,"uid":64345,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:13:40.000Z","msg":"趴趴走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好有動感。"},{"pid":"54c0ff2c5f1b3e13b799d37e8574b874392140d8","tid":2339813,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:14:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">中國新增14例確診 本土7例都在遼寧</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/12/25 08:55<br />\n<br />\n（中央社台北25日電）<span class=\"red\">中國官方今天通報，新增14例2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19）確診，其中有7例本土傳播，都來自遼寧省大連市，當地已連續多日出現本土病例。</span><br />\n<br />\n中國國家衛生健康委員會官網通報，24日零至24時，31個省（自治區、直轄市）和新疆生產建設兵團報告新增確診病例14例，其中境外移入7例（上海4例，遼寧1例，廣東1例，四川1例），本土7例（均在遼寧）；無新增死亡病例；無新增疑似病例。<br />\n<br />\n另據遼寧省衛健委網站，當地新增的7例本土個案都來自大連市，其中1例為無症狀感染者轉確診。大連市近日連續出現本土病例。<br />\n<br />\n截至24日24時，據31個省（自治區、直轄市）和新疆生產建設兵團報告，現有確診320例（其中重症6例），累計治癒出院8萬1959例，累計死亡4634例，累計報告確診8萬6913例，無現有疑似病例。累計追蹤到密切接觸者89萬7690人，尚在醫學觀察的密切接觸者9890人。<br />\n<br />\n港澳累計確診部分，<span class=\"red\">香港特別行政區8424例（死亡135例）</span>，澳門特別行政區46例（出院46例）。（編輯：周慧盈）1091225<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202012250024.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Facn%2F202012250024.aspx&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt0PclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=af1b7a54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202012250024.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"9c111f30be90b8fdb2c745280078223cdbbebf7b","tid":2339813,"uid":337052,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"110b8f49673ff690d1dea19d3c129515fe61fce4","tid":2339813,"uid":64345,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:13:40.000Z","msg":"趴趴走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好有動感。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:15:50.000Z","msg":"台語<br />\n趴趴走（p'a-p'a-tsauˋ）──到處亂跑"},{"pid":"21d2d4e0de3b8badaba0ad96b86c13385d2feddd","tid":2339813,"uid":355064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"110b8f49673ff690d1dea19d3c129515fe61fce4","tid":2339813,"uid":64345,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:13:40.000Z","msg":"趴趴走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好有動感。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:16:19.000Z","msg":"小蟲蟲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3cf3497c7f79713064eba65888bde9f4a934df","tid":2339813,"uid":323157,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:17:24.000Z","msg":"中国唔係清零咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fce1dd9237719a58586a20d2c817a15dc235524","tid":2339813,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:18:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BAIbfPLeZNQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBAIbfPLeZNQ&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt0PclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=e54674f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BAIbfPLeZNQ</a>"},{"pid":"5c20abee64ec4f76bc8631708acc9794f37b83ab","tid":2339813,"uid":283222,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:18:56.000Z","msg":"無症狀趴趴走，無脈搏病患者呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00d9080f996cdb0768c08ab213481bfdc43460c","tid":2339813,"uid":362459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:19:29.000Z","msg":"你d外國勢力又亂up 明明0感染"},{"pid":"2fb7ef25d6dd1733b3278f835fb90bf9d5bd57a7","tid":2339813,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:20:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ei2Yb_yfP8g\" data-sr-